# Customer Order Flow System — Implementation Plan

## Overview

Build a **complete customer ordering flow** that is **strictly isolated** from the existing Vero Admin Dashboard. Customers navigate through 5 pages (Landing → Customer Info → Product Order → Payment → Confirmation) to place orders. All customer routes live under `/api/public/*` (API) and `/order/*` (pages). Admin routes remain under their existing `/admin/*`, `/dashboard/*` paths with JWT protection.

> [!IMPORTANT]
> **Strict Isolation**: Customer pages use a completely separate EJS layout (`customer-layout`), separate CSS (`customer.css`), separate route files, and separate API prefix (`/api/public/*`). No admin middleware, no admin cookies, no admin navigation will ever be accessible from or linked to the customer flow.

