### 3. New Middleware

---

#### [NEW] [customerValidation.js](file:///d:/Vero-20-4vvv/middleware/customerValidation.js)

All validation rules for the customer order flow using `express-validator`:

- **`customerInfoRules`** — Full name, phone format (Egyptian `01x-xxx-xxxx`), address fields
- **`cartItemRules`** — Product ID format, quantity > 0, size validation
- **`promoCodeRules`** — Code format (alphanumeric, max 20 chars)
- **`paymentRules`** — Method enum, payment proof required for non-COD
- **`orderSubmitRules`** — Complete order payload validation
- **`validateCustomer`** — Result handler that returns JSON errors

All rules include:
- `.trim()` and `.escape()` for XSS prevention
- String length limits to prevent DoS
- Regex patterns for phone numbers
- Type checking for numbers
- ObjectId format validation for product references

